價格大幅上漲。試以模型圖例分析能源價格大幅上漲對物價水準與產
出的影響。（10分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5a057cbe0128", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111190", "c": "320", "s": "1404", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "國際經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "四", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "經建行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
